---
**Guidelines for Authors:**
- Manuscript should be 3000-5000 words (excluding references)
- Use 12-point Times New Roman font
- Double spacing throughout
- Page numbers and line numbers
- Follow APA citation style
- Include DOI for all referenced articles
- Tables and figures should be submitted as separate files
- High-resolution images (300 DPI minimum)